                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="gnrec" value="160 — Graph Node Index (DUAL PURPOSE)&#xa;collection: gn_{pid}&#xa;Schema:&#xa;  161  node_key VARCHAR(256) — PK&#xa;  162  neo4j_id VARCHAR(128) ★&#xa;  163  node_type VARCHAR(32) ∈ {Entity, Concept, Procedure, Step}&#xa;  164  text VARCHAR(2048) — textual signature&#xa;  165  embedding FLOAT_VECTOR(768) [IVF_FLAT, COSINE]&#xa;&#xa;★ Storing neo4j_id alongside the embedding is the key novel feature.&#xa;  Used for (a) write-time deduplication and (b) read-time anchoring." style="rounded=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontStyle=1" parent="1" vertex="1">
